@ConnectorWebServer_HostAddress = http://localhost:5049

### 注册设备（获取令牌）
POST {{ConnectorWebServer_HostAddress}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "deviceName": "TestDevice",
  "deviceType": 1,
  "preSharedKey": "change-me-in-production"
}

### 刷新令牌
POST {{ConnectorWebServer_HostAddress}}/api/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "accessToken": "YOUR_TOKEN_HERE"
}

### 查询设备状态
GET {{ConnectorWebServer_HostAddress}}/api/devices/status
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### 查询待处理消息
GET {{ConnectorWebServer_HostAddress}}/api/messages/pending
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
